      KLUDBCBCDBESBEZUATSBCKTUESABKMNLOPSACQR $.

  ${
    eq5s.1 $e |- ( A. z A. x x = y -> ph ) $.
    $( Rule that applies ~eq5 to antecedent. $)
    eq5s   $p |- ( A. x x = y -> ph ) $=
      ( weq wal eq5 syl ) BCFBGZJDGABCDHEI $.
